.Dd Jun 16, 2020
.Dt SPP 1
.Sh NAME
.Nm spp
.Nd simple pre-processor
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm spp
.Op Fl h
.Op Fl o Ar file
.Op Fl t Ar type
.Op Fl e Ar evalstr
.Op Fl s Ar prefixstr
.Op Fl l
.Op Fl L
.Op Fl n
.Op Fl v
.Op [test-(dir|file) ...]
.Sh DESCRIPTION
Simple preprocessor tool similar to PHP or CPP but focusing on simplicity,
ease to be embedded and used from the commandline or the API.
